How to use:
Select any member of a panel and run the tool.
The tool will select all the members on the panel.
The tool will work for three categories in Revit:
1- Structural Columns
2- Structural Framing
3- Structural Connectors

You need to install pyRevit to create buttons or you can install RevitPythonShell, paste the code and run. 
Please see repository README file.

A short recording for the tools:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WH0WGdV8cNQ&t
